                    <div style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;margin:0;padding-bottom:16px">
<figure style="width: 100%;padding-bottom:16px;text-align:left;margin:0">


